---
import cli_screenshot from '../assets/cliscreenshot.png';
---

<section>
    <div class="bg-[#C8F0F1] text-center px-4 py-8 md:px-8 md:py-16">
		<h2 class="pb-8 md:pb-12 text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold">See it in Action</h2>
		<img class="m-auto max-w-full h-auto px-4 md:px-8" src={cli_screenshot.src} alt="Screenshot of the CIB Mango Tree CLI" />
		<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-center mt-8 md:mt-12 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
			<div class="w-full md:w-1/2 text-left px-4 md:px-6 mb-6 md:mb-0">
				CIB Mango Tree makes social media bot detection simple for everyone.
				It begins with easy-to-run tests, the "low-hanging fruit," that help reveal
				clear signs of unsophisticated coordinated inauthentic behavior (CIB)
				in social media and online data.
			</div>
			<div class="w-full md:w-1/2 text-left px-4 md:px-6">
				As you move up the Mango Tree, our tests become more advanced,
				 helping experienced users tackle deeper, more complex cases of manipulation
			</div>
		</div>

	</div>
     <div class="bg-[#C8F0F1] h-16 md:h-32" style={{
        clipPath: 'ellipse(70% 70% at top)',
        WebkitClipPath: 'ellipse(70% 70% at top)'
        }
    }>
    </div>
</section>